<div class="container d-flex flex-wrap mt-5 flex-column" >
    <h1 class="serif">First Things First</h1>
    <p>Run this to start redis server for a perfect running application with Sidekiq.</p>
    <div class="d-flex">

        <p class="code me-3" style="width:21rem;" id="#p1">sudo service redis-server start</p>

        <button_to class="btn btn-WHITE" onclick="copyToClipboard('#p1')" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
